{% column %}
## A fresh gameplay experience {% id="nouvelles-features" %}

{% /column %}
{% /row %}

{% row columns="1/3 1/3 1/3" bottom_margin="margin-l" %}
{% column %}
### Enhanced Visuals

The game's interface is fully designed for native 720p resolution. Most graphical elements have been updated to match.

{% /column %}
{% column %}
### Pokémon Memory System

Your Pokémon remember moves they’ve learned throughout their journey, letting you adjust their movesets outside of battle.

{% /column %}
{% column %}
### Side Quests

Forêt Éternelle offers a wide range of side quests to deepen the lore behind your Pokémon partners.

{% /column %}
{% /row %}

{% row columns="1/3 1/3 1/3" bottom_margin="margin-l" %}
{% column %}
### Skill Tree

Choose from three unique branches to customize your gameplay style and unlock valuable bonuses.

{% /column %}
{% column %}
### Achievement System

Your actions unlock achievements that you can track and share with others in the community.

{% /column %}
{% column %}
### Daycare Monitoring

The Poké-Nav lets you monitor Pokémon left at the daycare from a distance — ideal for knowing when your eggs are ready.

{% /column %}
{% /row %}

{% row columns="1/1" bottom_margin="margin-l" %}
{% column %}
![Screenshot of a battle between two Pokémon invented for the game](./images/screen3_en.png)

{% /column %}
{% /row %}

{% row columns="1/1" bottom_margin="margin-l" %}
{% column %}
