{% /column %}
{% /row %}

{% row columns="1/1" bottom_margin="margin-l" %}
{% column %}
## Used technologies {% id="technos" %}

- Game Engine : **Pokémon SDK** & the **LiteRGSS** (Ruby 3.0.0)
- Default game screen size : **1280x720** pixels
- Audio Management Library : [FMOD](http://www.fmod.org/)
- Map editing : [Tiled](https://www.mapeditor.org/)
- Game data editing : **Pokémon Studio**
- Events editing : **RPG Maker XP**

{% /column %}
{% /row %}

{% row columns="1/1" bottom_margin="margin-l" %}
{% column %}
