- [**Level Designers**](https://www.pokemonforeteternelle.com/recruitment/en/4.png "Level Designers") - examples [here](https://www.pokemonforeteternelle.com/recruitment/en/4bis.png "here").
- [**Ruby Developers**](https://www.pokemonforeteternelle.com/recruitment/en/5.png "Ruby Developers").

